title: Fan has heart attack toward end of Michigan St-Michigan game
text: BING NEWS: Fan has heart attack toward end of Michigan St-Michigan game ANN ARBOR, Mich. (AP) A fan was treated for a heart attack and taken to a hospital after No. 7 Michigan State stunned No. 12 Michigan 27-23 on Saturday with a last-second score.
